{"tid":1865481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支那口交部指有國家過度反應無助防控疫情　已提出嚴正交涉","createTime":"2020-02-06T08:09:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T08:45:55.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"34e6018a66bf01d6815615c108f6414994c2a6e9","tid":1865481,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T08:09:12.000Z","msg":"在北京，外交部發言人華春瑩說，新型冠狀病毒感染肺炎的疫情發生後，中方採取最徹底及嚴格的防控舉措，正取得積極成效，中方對有關國家無視世衛組織專業權威的建議，不遵守國際民航組織的公告，表示不滿和反對，已提出嚴正交涉。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩說一些國家採取中斷航班等過度反應的措施，不單上無助防控疫情，反而人為製造恐慌，嚴重干擾國際正常人員往來及合作，干擾國際航空運輸市場的秩序，敦促有關國家糾正做法，以實際行動體現對中國抗擊疫情的支持。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩又說，中方對於在華外籍人士，特別是在湖北武漢外國公民的合理訴求，始終高度重視，積極採取有效措施，及時提供疫情資訊及相關諮詢，保障生活、防疫、治療等方面的需求。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507017-20200206.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507017-20200206.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsv3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=d7e4c394\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507017-20200206.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=85bb613b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507017-20200206.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"57d021a3a1c2527688d6a319e5f0e5bae412eef1","tid":1865481,"uid":51271,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T08:10:18.000Z","msg":"食少兩隻蝙蝠啦屌你老母口交部"},{"pid":"093eb8118624439d84eb48b3698dea7f6e7742a7","tid":1865481,"uid":71748,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T08:10:31.000Z","msg":"北韓同俄羅斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa9169705617136bb91597e6c77a2bf7249dbea","tid":1865481,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T08:10:53.000Z","msg":"同你契哥講啦柒頭"},{"pid":"39e8be674a69fa2b918a2734f818c48d44890dd8","tid":1865481,"uid":92353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"